title: #49: Sabina Gadecki -The Naked Show

description:
Actress, Model, & World Traveler Sabina Gadecki joins Lauryn & Michael to chat about the audition process for the "Entourage" movie, what it was like filming a nude scene for the first time, how she wound up dating Kevin Connolly, what the chaotic 'Pilot Season' is like, and she talks about the pressure to look a certain way while working in the film & modeling industry.
